summary: Ryume is the Beauty Dragon in the Skyrim
descriptionHtml:
Requirements
-Skyrim 1.9.32
-SKSE http://skse.silverlock.org/
-Racemenu https://www.nexusmods.com/skyrim/mods/29624/?
-ApachiiSkyhair https://www.nexusmods.com/skyrim/mods/10168/?
-MikanEyes https://www.nexusmods.com/skyrim/mods/56056/?
-HD Race https://www.nexusmods.com/skyrim/mods/72416/?
-Born Dragon Skin https://www.nexusmods.com/skyrim/mods/63680/?
-Animated Dragon Wings https://www.nexusmods.com/skyrim/mods/53271/?

[center]
Installation
copy "Ryume The Beauty Dragon.jslot" to "c:/program files/The Elder Scroll V Skyrim/Data/SKSE/Plugins/CharGen/Presets"
and how to load the preset???
-start the game
-open command console and type "showracemenu" without this " symbol
-and press F9 in the Preset menu
-Click "Ryume The Beauty Dragon.jslot" and accept
Done!!!


Need comment for my preset to upgrade it
Ty before :)[/center]



TY for who have the mods for my preset
